metadata.name: Alpha Wave Visions NFT Collection: Cosmic Brain #1
metadata.description: A collection of Audio-reactive generative art revealing the visions of those who tried the Alpha Wave Experience. A brain is breathing in the cosmos. Its shapes get transformed into particle coloured dust and come back to its original shape. Created by Alpha Wave Experience art collective. Generative Art: Dimitri Thouzery. Music: Toga Fidan / Dan Ghenacia
